Description: Pentesting environment with integrated shells and note-taking
 PenEnv is a modern GTK4 desktop application for managing penetration testing
 environments with integrated shells, note-taking, and target management.
 .
 Features:
  * Multiple shell tabs with full bash functionality
  * Tab completion and all terminal features
  * Target management with dropdown and popup selector
  * Auto-saving notes with markdown syntax highlighting
  * Command logging with automatic log refresh
  * Tab renaming and keyboard shortcuts
